OL,3,CArrest warrant issued for ex Co-op
OL,4,CBank chair
OL,6,FA judge has issued a warrant for the
OL,7,Farrest of disgraced former Co-
OL,8,Foperative Bank chairman Paul Flowers
OL,9,Fafter he failed to appear at court for
OL,10,Fhis fraud sentencing.
OL,12,FFlowers, 74, pleaded guilty in July
OL,13,F2024 to fraud amounting to nearly
OL,14,F#100,000, when he abused his position
OL,15,Fas the executor of the will and holder
OL,16,Fof power of attorney for a woman named
OL,17,FMargaret Jarvis.
