OL,4,CBank chair
OL,6,FManchester Crown Court has heard that
OL,7,FFlowers had "disengaged" with his
OL,8,Flegal team, although a solicitor had
OL,9,Fcontacted him on Thursday night to
OL,10,Fexplain the consequences of not
OL,11,Fattending court.
OL,13,FJudge Nicholas Dean KC, the Honorary
OL,14,FRecorder of Manchester, issued a
OL,15,Fwarrant not backed for bail.
