OL,3,CArrest warrant issued for ex Co-op
OL,4,CBank chair
OL,6,FFlowers, from Salford, was dubbed the
OL,7,F"Crystal Methodist" after the Mail on
OL,8,FSunday published secretly filmed
OL,9,Ffootage of the then-church minister
OL,10,Fhanding over #300 in cash for crystal
OL,11,Fmeth and other drugs in Leeds in
OL,12,FNovember 2013.
OL,14,FHe pleaded guilty at Leeds
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court to possessing
OL,16,Fcocaine, crystal meth and ketamine as
OL,17,Fwas fined #400.
