OL,6,FEarlier that year, Flowers had stood
OL,7,Fdown as chairman of the Co-Operative
OL,8,FBank, a post he had held for more than
OL,9,Fthree years, after a #1.5 billion
OL,10,Fblack hole was discovered in its
OL,11,Ffinances.
OL,13,FThe former Labour councillor in
OL,14,FRochdale and Bradford was later banned
OL,15,Ffrom the financial services industry
OL,16,Fafter the City watchdog found he
OL,17,Fdemonstrated the "lack of fitness and
OL,18,Fpropriety required" to work in the
OL,19,Fsector.
